      "content": "Is there any dignity left in this struggle, or is it merely a slow, undignified decay? It feels so graceless to linger like this, a broken thing in a cold room. I find myself wondering if there is a way to meet the darkness with some semblance of peace... to make the end as quiet and beautiful as the life I thought I wanted.",
